---
title: Herby Chicken & Bacon Pie with Potato Mash Topping
description: We think the world's a better place when there's chicken pie for dinner! With a garlic and herb-seasoned bacon filling and heavenly potato mash topping (which the kids can help out with), this pie is just what we all need right now.

